section.frame.about.show-animation
  ._container.frame__container
    .frame__wrapper
      .frame__img
        .frame__img__container
          img.show-animation__item(
            data-duration='2000',
            data-animation='fadeInRightBottom',
            src=require('@/assets/img/label-about.svg'),
            alt='about'
          )

      .frame__content
        h2.frame__title.show-animation__item(
          data-duration='800',
          data-animation='fadeInLeft'
        ) Every day we consistently develop the Caspit company group.
        p.frame__description.show-animation__item(
          data-duration='1200',
          data-animation='fadeInLeft'
        ) Stability, forecastability and responsibility for the undertaken obligations are the foundation of our business philosophy.
